            <div class="how-step-desc">Buyers discover listings through three-layer context retrieval: Layer 1 (Redis + SQLite session state), Layer 2 (AgentHandoffMemory — ~61% token savings for multi-agent context), and Layer 3 (pgvector semantic search with SQLite fallback). SOVA tool <code>semantic_listing_search</code> (#72) queries all three layers. The unified dispatcher at <code>POST /marketplace/action</code> routes all 14 action types.</div>
