            <div class="how-step-desc">Every incoming negotiation passes through the <code>BrandAgentFilter</code> — four fail-open gates in sequence: deny-list check, TrustRank scoring (<code>BRAND_AGENT_MIN_TRUST=0.0</code> default, disables TrustRank until reputation data exists), per-agent rate limit, and capability matching. The First-Proposal Bias Guard enforces a minimum of 3 evaluated alternatives before purchase, ranked by <code>price × (1 - rep_score)</code> utility — not arrival order.</div>
